<br>
Now, let me flip the oil - ethanol problem around so it relates to the Drug War.<br>
We have multi-billion dollar corporations that pay hundreds of millions of dollars in taxes each year so you don't get a headache. Because they make so much money for the government, the government has deemed these drugs as good, and we're free to use them as long as our doctors say so.<br>
However, there are bad drugs too. Those are drugs that:<br>
<br>
